RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 1 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 49. Allowance Purse 4000. FOR CERTIFIED NORTH DAKOTA BRED THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: REAL CRAFTY PIE Broke well, took lead, drew away. LENNOX THE GREAT contended all the way. DEPUTY VERDOT late gain for show. ELI'S FIRE broke well, contended, tired. MR. ADVENTUROUS never a contender.

ENTRY.NAME: Real Crafty Pie
ENTRY.COMMENT: Broke well, took lead, drew away

RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 2 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 56. Maiden Special Weight Purse 4500. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.

ENTRY.COMMENT: jockey pulled up first turn, loped in

RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 3 350 Y Dirt CR: 66. Allowance Purse 4500. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MOUNTAINS ARE BLUE Broke well, drew away. DCR ALL FIRED UP Gamely. JJ EXEL Gamely. GABRIELS WAY Improved effort. LIZS SPECIAL COPY No menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 4 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 77. Allowance Purse 4700. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: OUR PETUNIA A runaway. TIPSY AT THE BAR Followed winner. DIVA DE KELA Followed place. CHAMA no menace. A BUNCH FOR LUNCH Stopped.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: Chippewa Downs Mixed Derby Final CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 5 350 Y Dirt CR: 68. Final Purse 9200. For Three year old Quarter Horses, Paints and Apaloosas that are Certified North Dakota Breds that qualified in trials.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: KGS WISH Dueled, Big finish. REDOINIT Broke on top, caught, game effort. KOOL CHARLY competed, good effort. VOLCOMS SHADOW rail trip. ONE PAINTED SPITFIRE erratic trip. JENNAS QUICK JESS lugged in. BP PHOENIX TO WIN no menace. FERGIES HAPPY fractious in gate, trailed.

ENTRY.NAME: Redoinit
ENTRY.COMMENT: Broke on top, caught, game effort

RACE.RACE_TEXT: NDTA Maturity CHIPPEWA DOWNS RACE 7 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 72. Stakes Purse 10000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLD AND OLDER THOROUGHBREDS THAT ARE CERTIFIED NORTH DAKOTA BREDS AND OWNED BY MEMBERS OF THE NORTH DAKOTA THOROUGHBRED ASSOCIATION. HIGH WEIGHTS PREFERRED.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: KREWS PASS Total runaway. TRICKY KID Followed winner. BONNIE AND mid pack thruout. RAILROAD DAN passed tiring foes. EMMITT'S CHALLENGE Set pace early, tired. BIG ENDER Trailed.
